{"tid":443184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隱居石屋無人問　獨居男子化白骨","createTime":"2017-10-21T11:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T15:19:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd8ea62d3890ce9c67795929961fe40d39410c9","tid":443184,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171021/large/1508564257_be2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171021%2Flarge%2F1508564257_be2e.jpg&h=091746c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上午10時左右，有掃墓人士在荃灣上花山一間石屋內，發現人形骸骨，慌忙報警。警方到場調查，在屋內撿獲證件和雜物，初步相信是一名獨居男子所有。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子隱居石屋最少半年，之前一度被村民誤以為是非法入境者，報警調查，經警員了解他有本港身份證，並有精神病紀錄。警方相信骸骨是此名獨居漢，疑死後一直不被發現。"},{"pid":"fffe4df7c17d40e25522f65dc819e36094ff9420","tid":443184,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171021&amp;guid=57358777&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171021%26guid%3D57358777%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Mu%2F1q9CTjYjE6LpYEkMUJQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=aba7bb42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171021%26guid%3D57358777%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=fd815d91\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171021&amp;guid=57358777&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"170db5d44414dc7ae2dab4ef1a8abc6dd166c616","tid":443184,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"獨居不被發現， 正常。"},{"pid":"b3afff14f9c63ea67c75c1c954f8e78e0eebf0a3","tid":443184,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"邊個連登仔？"},{"pid":"22dfc3d1b8d85561243f8bdad121c42cbb7d5732","tid":443184,"uid":154872,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T11:45:29.000Z","msg":"樓豬怕唔怕自己收尾幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b3e2256d3a9f69f8e8fab7ac065691d5cb2933","tid":443184,"uid":86938,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"點解個掃墓人士會無啦啦走入去間屋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895462d3ae759d642356f846bc273d00126937b0","tid":443184,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獨撚"},{"pid":"5dee0bb4a81e8b07b1f280c9dc13ae17d9dd6ca8","tid":443184,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b95db0ac87e473022eab523d8ef160da1064b0c9","tid":443184,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2364a5a6b2ac72d9e71bed0c6a4a815cfab0d39","tid":443184,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0ea5e72b73403ca9bbe60a48dd5f2f19a783454","tid":443184,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔的結局"},{"pid":"270bad624e58bab4114b0f2ee205fc929bdf18fb","tid":443184,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"其實福氣黎，一個人黎，一個人走，冇虧欠人"}]}